  <h2>The Challenge</h2>
  <div class="side-by-side">
    <p>
      1. P3 wanted to go beyond standard sponsorship—this wasn’t just about logo
      placements or product shots. The challenge was to authentically integrate
      P3 into real UFC fighter routines, making it feel like a natural part of
      their training lifestyle.
    </p>
    <p>
      2. The features needed to highlight the fighters first, the brand
      second—ensuring that P3’s message was woven into the storytelling, rather
      than feeling like a traditional ad.
    </p>
  </div>
