<div>
  <h2>The Solution</h2>
  <p class="big">A Documentary Approach to Brand Storytelling</p>
  <p>
    Each feature was shot and edited in a cinematic, behind-the-scenes style,
    giving fans an intimate look at the fighters’ daily lives. With my
    experience in documentary storytelling, it felt like a natural fit to
    gravitate towards this style of storytelling, using training footage,
    personal interviews, and high-energy fight prep sequences to make the
    content feel raw and real.
  </p>
  <p>
    Instead of forced product placement, P3 was naturally embedded into the
    fighters’ nutrition routines, gym sessions, and on-the-go
    moments—reinforcing its role as a performance-focused brand.
  </p>
</div>

